    <name>Doom64EX</name>
    <summary>Recreation of Midway's Doom64 for modern operating systems</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            Doom 64 is a Doom spin-off for the Nintendo 64.
        </p>
        <p>
            Doom64EX is a faithful recreation of the original Nintendo 64 game using
            PC Doom's source code as the base.
        </p>
        <p>
            Doom64EX requires the data files from the original game.
        </p>
    </description>

    <url type="homepage">https://github.com/svkaiser/Doom64EX</url>
    <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/svkaiser/Doom64EX/issues</url>

